    Failure Threshold
      √ transitions CLOSED -> OPEN after failure threshold (2 ms)
      √ counts consecutive failures correctly (1 ms)
    Cooldown and Half-Open
      √ calculates cooldown remaining (2 ms)
      √ allows limited calls in half-open state (1 ms)
    Success Recovery
      √ transitions HALF-OPEN -> CLOSED after success threshold (2 ms)
    Per-Agent Isolation
      √ has separate breakers for different agents (2 ms)
      √ returns existing breaker from cache
    execute() wrapper
      √ executes successful function
      √ blocks execution when open (14 ms)
      √ tracks metrics during execute
    DB Persistence
      √ persists state to database (3 ms)
      √ loads state from database on construction (2 ms)
    resetBreaker
      √ resets breaker to closed state (3 ms)
