    Queries
      √ lists quarantined agents (4 ms)
      √ provides statistics (2 ms)
    Department Quarantine
      √ quarantines all agents in a department (11 ms)
    DB Persistence
      √ persists quarantine to DB (2 ms)
      √ updates agent status in agents table (1 ms)
  Level 3 - Workflow Stop
    Stop Workflow
      √ stops a running workflow (2 ms)
      √ does not stop already stopped workflow (3 ms)
      √ does not stop completed workflow (1 ms)
      √ does not stop failed workflow (2 ms)
    Data Preservation
      √ preserves step information on stop (2 ms)
      √ preserves status as stopped in DB (2 ms)
    Resume Workflow
      √ resumes a stopped workflow (2 ms)
      √ restores previous status on resume (3 ms)
      √ fails to resume non-stopped workflow (1 ms)
    Enforcement
      √ enforceWorkflow throws for stopped workflow (4 ms)
      √ enforceWorkflow does not throw for running workflow (1 ms)
      √ WorkflowStoppedError has correct properties (2 ms)
    Stop Unit
      √ stops all workflows in a unit (5 ms)
      √ does not match partial unit IDs (security) (3 ms)
      √ handles JSON arrays for responsible_agents (3 ms)
    DB Persistence
      √ logs stopped workflow to DB (2 ms)
  Level 4 - Global Kill Switch
    Confirmation Code
      √ requires confirmation code to activate (4 ms)
      √ activates with correct confirmation code (1 ms)
      √ uses correct confirmation code constant (1 ms)
    Permission Check
      √ only founder can activate
      √ allows activation in test environments (2 ms)
    Kill Switch State
