    DB Persistence
      √ persists activation to DB (1 ms)
      √ persists system settings (2 ms)
    Statistics
      √ provides activation statistics (2 ms)
    requireConfirmationCode
      √ always requires confirmation code
  Integration - All 4 Levels
    √ Level 1 can escalate to Level 2 (3 ms)
    √ Level 4 blocks all agent operations (4 ms)
    √ each level operates independently (4 ms)
  Safety - Security Critical
